I don't know the details of lambda well but does it not allow something like
CompletableFuture<Foo> response = backend.getFoo();

response.thenAccept(writeToOutputStream);

If this is allowed than I think we need to make sure the span survives until the output is closed since that's the length of the request and how we generally model async requests.

